text: Hit Parade of 1943 is a 1943 American musical movie directed by Albert S. Rogell and starring John Carroll, Susan Hayward, Gail Patrick, Eve Arden, Melville Cooper, Mary Treen, Walter Catlett, Addison Richards. It was distributed by Republic Pictures and was nominated for 2 Academy Awards in 1944. ==Other websites== * * * Category:1943 musical movies Category:American musical movies Category:Movies directed by Albert S. Rogell
title: Hit Parade of 1943
